      *  DFTTSTAMPC - Create a Default Timestamp for an OPM Program.  *
      *                                                               *
      *  This /COPY initialises a field called TSTAMP (26A) with the  *
      *  default 0001-01-01-00.00.00.000000 timestamp value.          *
      *                                                               *
