      *  Prev Amend No. nnnnnn             Date ddmmmyy               *
      *                                                               *
      *---------------------------------------------------------------*
      *                                                               *
      *  178802 - New /COPY created for this fix.                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
      * Create a default timestamp in the correct structure
      *
     C                     MOVEL'0001-01-'WHKTM1 16
     C                     MOVE '01-00.00'WHKTM1
     C                     MOVELWHKTM1    WHKTM2 24
     C                     MOVE '.00.0000'WHKTM2
     C                     MOVELWHKTM2    WHKTM3 26
     C                     MOVE '00'      WHKTM3
     C                     MOVE WHKTM3    TSTAMP 26
      *
      *****************************************************************
      * End of /COPY DFTTSTAMPC                                       *
